    "### Transformer Memory Characteristics:\n",
    "- **Attention**: Low arithmetic intensity (~10-100 FLOPs/byte), memory-bound\n",
    "- **Linear layers**: High arithmetic intensity (~1000+ FLOPs/byte), compute-bound\n",
    "- **Softmax**: Very low arithmetic intensity (~1-10 FLOPs/byte), extremely memory-bound\n",
